title: THE Steve Wilkos Show 06.18.08
description:
I MOLESTED MY DAUGHTER:

    A daughter&#039;s trust betrayed... Twelve years ago Harold took his 14-year-old daughter Charlene out drinking, and by the end of the night, both their lives would forever change. Harold claims in a drunken state, he accidentally mistook his daughter for somebody else, and tried to make a move on her, but nothing happened. Charlene however, tells a darker tale where her father not only took advantage of her, but tried to rape her. After eight years of prison, Harold continues to deny these charges, but Steve&#039;s had enough denial, and he wants the truth!
